Perl Module distribution WWW::Ebay

Allows you to do stuff on ebay.com that requires you to log in, such as:

* Search completed auctions
* Search mature categories
* Retrieve your watch-list from your "my eBay" page
* Retrieve your active auctions from your "my eBay" page

For more information about my Perl Modules, 
visit http://www.sandcrawler.com/SWB/cpan-modules.html

mthurn at cpan.org
